data.description: Motivated Seller! This beautiful 5 bedroom 2.5 bath two-story home is located in the North Central Belton Historic District in the Alexander and Hanna subdivision. The first floor has 3 living space areas, a dine-in kitchen, and a laundry room. From the kitchen, you can see the back living room as well as the main living room area. The back living area is a large enclosed porch and the laundry room is an enclosed carport with plenty of storage space. The kitchen includes a refrigerator purchased in April 2022 and a Samsung gas oven purchased in June 2022. Upstairs there are 5 bedrooms, one room is an enclosed balcony that could be used for an office space or a functional bedroom. The master suite has a huge walk-in closet that leads to the master bath. This beautiful home has a beautiful backyard. Schedule your private showing today!
